&34 . :
&35 - _

# Space and modifiers
&39   &20 &20

# Symbols
SYM &80 &3C &42 &40 &7C &40 &42 &3C &00  # Euro
SYM &A7 &3C &40 &3C &42 &3C &02 &7C &00  # Section
SYM &B0 &18 &24 &24 &18 &00 &00 &00 &00  # Degree
SYM &B4 &08 &10 &00 &00 &00 &00 &00 &00  # Acute accent
SYM &C4 &00 &24 &00 &3C &42 &7E &42 &00  # A diaeresis
SYM &D6 &00 &24 &00 &3C &42 &42 &3C &00  # O diaeresis
SYM &DC &00 &24 &00 &42 &42 &42 &3E &00  # U diaeresis
SYM &DF &00 &3C &42 &7C &42 &42 &7C &40  # Eszett
SYM &E4 &00 &24 &00 &3C &02 &3E &46 &00  # A diaeresis lowercase
SYM &F6 &00 &24 &00 &3C &42 &42 &3C &00  # O diaeresis lowercase
SYM &FC &00 &24 &00 &42 &42 &42 &3E &00  # U diaeresis lowercase
